└── README.md                # This file
```

## Testing

The package includes a comprehensive test script (`main.py`) that demonstrates:

1. Basic tree creation and printing
2. Adding nodes by path
3. Building trees from YAML files
4. Editing node values
5. Writing trees to YAML files
6. Printing nodes in a range
7. Deleting specific nodes
8. Deleting entire trees

